        public String getWeightName()
        The name of the weight profile used while calculating during extraction phase. In many cases, this will return DirectionsCriteria.WEIGHT_NAME_ROUTABILITY, DirectionsCriteria.WEIGHT_NAME_DURATION, or DirectionsCriteria.WEIGHT_NAME_DISTANCE.
        Returns:
        a String representing the weight profile used while calculating the route.
